### Subqueries Cont.

- Can include subqueries wherever I want within in the SELECT, FROM, WHERE clauses
    -  Queries can become long an complicated. Make sure to properly format them.
    -  Annotate and properly indent them when possible.
- Subqueries can be cumbersome on computing power, look for other more efficent ways to pull data before relying on this.
- Watch any filters that I have. Need to be in evey query.


